OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban delayed in Jersey
OL,4,Cafter legal error
OL,6,FThe sale and supply of disposable
OL,7,Fvapes will continue to be legal in
OL,8,FJersey following an error in the
OL,9,Flegislation designed to outlaw them.
OL,11,FThe ban was expected to start on
OL,12,FSunday 1 June, in line with a move by
OL,13,Fthe UK, but officials included the
OL,14,Fwrong words in the law change, meaning
OL,15,Fit has to go through another approval
OL,16,Fprocess.
