OL,6,FThe legal mistake, referring to the
OL,7,FRoyal Court rather than the
OL,8,FMagistrates Court, was discovered
OL,9,Fafter the amendment had already been
OL,10,Fsigned off by politicians and the
OL,11,FPrivy Council.
OL,13,FWriting to affected businesses,
OL,14,FInfrastructure Minister, Connetable
OL,15,FAndy Jehan, says this error "has
OL,16,Fresulted in a delay of a few months as
OL,17,Fthe new amendment was drafted, lodged
OL,18,Fand debated".
