OL,6,FThat redrafted law change was passed
OL,7,Fby politicians at the end of April and
OL,8,Fwill now go back to the Privy Council
OL,9,Ffor approval.
OL,11,FSelling, importing and supplying
OL,12,Fdisposable vapes became a criminal
OL,13,Foffence in Guernsey in April 2024.
OL,15,FJersey's States Assembly initially
OL,16,Fapproved the ban on single-use vapes
OL,17,Funanimously in December 2024, which
OL,18,Fwas subsequently accepted by the Privy
OL,19,FCouncil and registered in the Royal
OL,20,FCourt on Friday 21 March.
