OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban delayed in Jersey
OL,4,Cafter legal error
OL,6,FThe error means the corrected
OL,7,Famendment is expected to be approved
OL,8,Fby the Privy Council around the end of
OL,9,FJune.
OL,11,FConnetable Jehan explains the
OL,12,FGovernment now expects the ban to come
OL,13,Finto force in July or August, followed
OL,14,Fby a six-month sell-through period to
OL,15,Fallow retailers to clear their
OL,16,Fexisting stock.
OL,18,FHe adds that Jersey businesses will be
OL,19,Funable to buy disposable vapes from UK
OL,20,Fcompanies once their ban comes into
OL,21,Fplace.
