OL,6,FWhat about the UK ban?
OL,8,FEngland, Scotland, Wales and Northern
OL,9,FIreland are still banning the sale and
OL,10,Fsupply of single-use vapes from Sunday
OL,11,F1 June 2025, with no sell-through
OL,12,Fperiod.
OL,14,FBetween 2012 and 2023, vape usage in
OL,15,FEngland grew by more than 400%, with
OL,16,Fover 9% of people buying and using
OL,17,Fvapes.
